365
00:16:13,089 --> 00:16:15,923
Pork chops with
my secret seasoning.

366
00:16:15,925 --> 00:16:20,094
<i>Yeah, you do like your
secrets, don't you, Marge?</i>

367
00:16:20,096 --> 00:16:22,129
